---
title: Parmesan-Crusted Baked Shrimp with Buttered Rice and Lemony Mayo
description: Beautiful shrimp fillets topped with Parmesan and a generous heap of herbed panko bake to perfection! A touch of lemon mayo takes this fish dinner to the next level, and basmati rice and green beans are simple, satisfying sides.
